      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a 3.64:1 limited-slip differential. Mechanically sound, this example has undergone critical subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The chassis remains sharp with refreshed bushings and a balanced 50/50 weight distribution, offering the precise feedback and analog engagement that defines this generation's performance benchmark. A mechanically honest driver\u2019s car optimized for the enthusiast.",
